you can use this program in 3 ways
1. to list the special contents in the given directory
$ python copyspecial.py "exact directory address"

2. to copy the special contents into a given directory
$ python copyspecial.py '--todir' "directory address to copy,dir1" "directory address to search for the special contents, dir2"
the program will search for the special contents in the dir2, if such special contents are there, the program will copy those contents to dir1

3. compress(zip) the files to a given directory
$ python copyspecial.py '--tozip' "where to zip" "search fpr the special contents"



